text: Seydou Elimane Diarra (23 November 1933"Le gouvernement de transition de Côte d'Ivoire formé le 4 janvier 2000" , Afrique Express . – 19 July 2020) was an Ivorian politician. He was the Prime Minister in 2000 and again from 2003 to 2005. Diarra was born in Katiola, French West Africa. Diarra died on 19 July 2020 in Abidjan, Cote d'Ivoire at the age of 86.L’ancien premier ministre ivoirien, Seydou Diarra, est mort ==References== Category:1933 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Ambassadors Category:Prime ministers of Ivory Coast Category:African diplomats
